    "en": {
      "title": "Long queues for fuel at LIOC filling stations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lankans can be seen waiting in long queues for fuel, leading to the nearest Lanka IOC filling station, as the country struggles to contain a deepening economic crisis.",
        "Many tense situations have taken a place in several filling stations due to the lack of fuel.",
        "As a result, on Wednesday (6) a man from Digana climbed onto a post attached to high-voltage electricity cables to protest.",
        "Later, this man was rescued by personnel attached to the Ceylon Electricity Board and was rushed to the Theldeniya Hospital for treatment."
      ],
